import { useRoutes } from 'react-router-dom';



const AdminRoutes = () => useRoutes(
	
		<Route element={<LayoutAdmin/>}>
          <Route path="/admin" element={<Home/>}/>
          <Route path="/admin/quan-ly-nguoi-dung" element={<Users/>}/>
          <Route path="/admin/quan-ly-bai-dang" element={<Posts/>}/>
          <Route path="/admin/bao-cao" element={<Report/>}/>
          <Route path="/admin/quan-ly-danh-muc" element={<Categories/>}/>
          <Route path="/admin/cai-dat" element={<Setting/>}/>
          <Route path="/admin/xem-chi-tiet-bai-dang/:id" element={<PostDetail/>}/>
           <Route path="/admin/them-danh-muc" element={<AddCategory/>}/>
          <Route path="/admin/quan-ly-binh-luan" element={<Comments/>}/>
          <Route path="/admin/quan-ly-cong-thuc" element={<Recipes/>}/>
          <Route path="/admin/xem-chi-tiet-cong-thuc/:id" element={<RecipeDetail/>}/>
          <Route path="/admin/sua-danh-muc/:slug" element={<EditCategory/>}/>
      </Route>
	
);

export default AdminRoutes;
